response = self.app.post('/login', data={'email': self.user, 'password':
    self.password, 'api': self.api.upper()})
headers = self.response_to_headers(response)
response = self.app.get(self.api.lower() + '/movies', headers=headers)
self.assertEqual(response.status_code, 200)
response = self.app.post('/logout', headers=headers, data={'api': self.api.
    capitalize()})
self.assertEqual(response.status_code, 204)
